    <title>BAPI_GOODSMVT_CREATE How to goods receipt with reservation ?</title>
    <updated>2024-07-16T06:09:29.372000+02:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>SAP203</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/855363</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;I try to simulate MIGO goods receipt with the reference reservation number.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;the BAPI is still returned&amp;nbsp;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;EM&gt;E M7 096 Goods movement not possible with mvmt type 951. &lt;/EM&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;Please see below coding.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Could you give advise for this goods receipt ?&lt;/P&gt;&lt;pre class="lia-code-sample language-abap"&gt;&lt;code&gt;LS_HEADER-PSTNG_DATE = '20240716'.
LS_HEADER-DOC_DATE   = '20240716'.
LS_HEADER-REF_DOC_NO = 'test'.

LT_ITEM-MATERIAL  = 'ABC10001'.
LT_ITEM-PLANT     = '1000'.
LT_ITEM-STGE_LOC  = '3003'.
LT_ITEM-MOVE_TYPE = '951'.
LT_ITEM-ENTRY_QNT = '1'.
LT_ITEM-ENTRY_UOM = 'KG'.
LT_ITEM-RESERV_NO = '0000019703'.
LT_ITEM-RES_ITEM  = '0001'.
APPEND LT_ITEM.

CALL FUNCTION 'BAPI_GOODSMVT_CREATE'
  EXPORTING
    GOODSMVT_HEADER  = LS_HEADER
    GOODSMVT_CODE    = '05'
    TESTRUN          = 'X'
  IMPORTING
    GOODSMVT_HEADRET = LS_HEADRET
  TABLES
    GOODSMVT_ITEM    = LT_ITEM
    RETURN           = LT_RETURN.&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
